name: Local5
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Your Local 5 Flash Briefing is the best source for Northeast Wisconsin's latest Weather, News, and Sports updates.

Updated multiple times a day and voiced by the anchors you know and trust, WFRV's Local 5 skill is as good as it gets when you want to stay in the local-know.

Click "Enable", go to Settings, and move Local 5 to the top of your Flash Briefing.

Have an idea to improve your experience? Email us at alexa@wearegreenbay.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
